column1: Another MS translate test with a var tag. This time the <var varname=""></var> attribute has empty quotes after it instead of just an empty variable name attribute like the last attempt.
OK, let's try this embedded variable one more time. I told <var username=""></var> to get to karate on Monday. This time, we're using Microsoft translate.
These phrases should be translated into machine translations using v3 of the Microsoft Translate API.
